description: Collection of the objects from the Yemeni museums The digital cataloguing of the South Arabian inscriptions and artefacts housed in the Yemeni museums is one of the activities of the project CASIS, funded by the Italian Ministry for the University and Research for the years 2007-2010. See also: Digital Archive for the Study of pre-Islamic Arabian Inscriptions
